data.description: Well maintained home with tons of natural light and an inground pool just in time for the summer!!  This spacious home is perfect for entertaining as it features 4 large bedrooms, a formal dining, den, and living area, with a wood burning fireplace! Freshly painted inside and out with new carpet throughout. The eat in kitchen has tons of cabinetry and over looks the fully fenced back yard with a pool and above ground hot tub!  Just on the other side of the iron fence is one of two Carriage Oaks ponds which are available to residents for fishing, canoeing, or just to enjoy all that nature has to offer. Located in an excellent school district and just minutes away from 1-20 and the Airline Drive Corridor.
